1. *Tražim* da odemo na izlet (I'm asking to go on a trip).
2. Da li *tražiš* odgovore? (Are you searching for answers?)
3. On *traži* da mu pomognemo (He is asking for help).
4. *Tražimo* sreću na svim našim putovanjima (We are seeking for happiness in all of our travels).
5. Oni *traže* novi dom (They are looking for a new home). 
6. *Tražila* sam da mi daš odgovor (I asked for an answer).
7. *Tražio* je pomoć (He requested help).
8. *Tražili* smo pravi put (We were looking for the right way).